<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Langston_Hughes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Major plays">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Major plays</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Don%27t_you_want_to_be_free.jpg" class="image" title="Don't You Want to Be Free? (1938) by Langston Hughes was performed for his Harlem Suitcase Theatre in Harlem, New York City."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ea/Don%27t_you_want_to_be_free.jpg/180px-Don%27t_you_want_to_be_free.jpg" width="180" height="288" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Don%27t_you_want_to_be_free.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<b>Don't You Want to Be Free?</b> (1938) by Langston Hughes was performed for his Harlem Suitcase Theatre in <a href="/wiki/Harlem" title="Harlem">Harlem</a>, <a href="/wiki/New_York_City" title="New York City">New York City</a>.</div>
